Europa Universalis IV Conquest Of Paradise [MULTI4] [Expansion] [FLT]

Europa Universalis IV: Conquest of Paradise is the first expansion for the game heavy critically acclaimed Europa Universalis IV, focusing on the exploration of the New World and the Native American nations empire. The expansion allows you to send their ships to the west and discover a new world unlike any you've seen before - for the first time in a game of Paradox Development Studio, you are given the option to discover a continent completely random. Conquest of Paradise also offers the ability to play as a Native American nation and master the mechanics of the federation and national ideas that are unique to the nations. The age of exploration is brought to life in this epic game of trade, diplomacy, war and exploration by Paradox Development Studio, the Masters of the Strategy. Europa Universalis IV gives you control of a nation to govern and to build an empire that lasts through the ages.
